title: You Appear Normal - EP 1
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES! In this episode the BABES chat about everything from weird Dad stories to the secrets of strawberries!


Subscribe to our Patreon! @ Patreon.com/nopreshnetwork to watch all the full length videos. Only one full episodes video will hit YouTube each month, the rest are exclusive to our Patreon. The audio version will ALWAYS be FREE and will be available on all listening platforms.

Learn more about your ad choices. Visit megaphone.fm/adchoices
